narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Not an exciting class, take it cause you have to.

Do not take this course. I disregarded people's warnings and it ruined my semester. It is tons of work to learn useless information that you weren't even rewarded for understanding because the partial credit is so stingy. They expect you to read their minds and know how they want you to explain things on tests and homeworks. If you can avoid it, do not take this course. Just so you know the logistics, it's weekly psets, 2 midterms and a final.
Take it if you have to but otherwise don't.
Do your p-sets making sure you have enough time first.
